# Running RSpec / Bundler / Rails commands

Do not attempt to run rspec or any database commands on your own.

<!-- The sandboxed shell used by the agent misconfigures the Ruby environment for this
repo. Before running `bundle`, `rspec`, or `rails` commands, fix the environment
in the same command:

1. **Unset the sandbox's injected `BUNDLE_PATH`.** It points at an empty temp
   cache dir (`.../cursor-sandbox-cache/.../bundle`), which breaks `bundle exec`
