## New/pending migrations

If a spec references a table from a migration that hasn't been applied to the
test database yet, you'll see `PG::UndefinedTable: relation "..." does not
exist`. Fix by migrating the test DB before running specs:

```bash
export PATH="$HOME/.rubies/ruby-3.4.9/bin:$PATH"; unset BUNDLE_PATH; RAILS_ENV=test bundle exec rails db:migrate
``` -->
